<h2>Access</h2>
<p> <span class="link-mailto"><a href="mailto:demorequest@bikalabs.com?subject=Access%20to%20Gaob%20Bika%20LIMS%203%20on-line%20installation"><u>Bika LIMS 3 demo request</u></a></span><strong><br /></strong></p>
<h2>Feedback</h2>
<p>Don't hesitate to post questions and comment to the Bika mailing lists: <a class="external-link" href="https://groups.google.com/forum/?hl=en#%21forum/bika-design">LIMS design</a>, <a class="external-link" href="http://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/bika-users">Users</a> or <a class="external-link" href="http://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/bika-developers">Developers</a>.</p>
<p>Please log issues, feature requests, or bug reports in the <a class="external-link" href="https://github.com/bikalabs/Bika-LIMS/issues">public issue tracker</a> at Github</p>
<div align="center"><a class="external-link" href="http://www.richemp.org.za/"><img src="http://www.bikalabs.com/images/umhlathuze" alt="" /></a></div>
<p>New items sponsored by the water quality lab at the City of uMhlathuze (COU), Richards Bay:</p>
<blockquote>
<a class="external-link" href="bika_setup/bika_calculations">Configurable results calculations</a>,    including interim fields and dependent results, are completely user    configurable now and new calculations can be added by authorised users    without requiring programming skills<br /><br />Dormant setup items can be de-activated, which will remove them from general view while maintaining database integrity<br /><br />Other COU sponsored enhancements include various worksheet and QC handling improvements and cancellation workflows for samples and analysis requests<br /><br /></blockquote>
<p align="center">***</p>
<p class="discreet">Plone 4's versioning is used to  maintain references to historical
data, and working copy support combined with a built-in content locking mechanism allow multiple users to access data without conflicts.&nbsp; Further workflow separation now   takes care of assigning analyses to worksheets, and to differentiate ARs    and worksheets awaiting file attachments. Using AJAX, Plone 4's further improved user interface and   a host of     smaller enhancements, many clicks were saved and  general    performance   improved</p>
<p class="discreet">The Plone catalog and indexes are being re-organised into  more LIMS  specific   indexes,   to further improve performance</p>
<p align="center"><a class="external-link" href="https://www.ohloh.net/p/bika"><img class="image-inline" src="bika-code-analysis-by-ohloh" alt="Bika code analysis by OHLOH" /></a></p>
<p align="center"><a class="external-link" href="https://www.ohloh.net/p/bika">Bika code analysis at Ohloh.net</a></p>
<h3>Code repository</h3>
<p>Fresh code is always available at <a href="https://github.com/bikalabs/Bika-LIMS">https://github.com/bikalabs/Bika-LIMS</a>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><a class="external-link" href="http://www.bikalabs.com/softwarecenter/bika/releases/3.0">Bika 3 Project page</a></strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a class="external-link" href="https://bika.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/bika/bika3"><br /></a></p>
